a friend can see each other in the real world ,via the Oculus Quest\u2019s cameras, and battle in AR.\n\n***NOTE:  Saber City is a multiplayer game and requires 2 Meta Quest headsets to play.\n\nIMPORTANT: Please maintain at least 3 feet distance between yourself and the other player. Be aware of your surroundings. Do not run with the headset on.\n\nYou can choose from 4 different character battle kits with unique weapons to wield in mixed reality. The current version of Saber City includes support for Meta Quest Pro and Quest 3.\n\nBattle Kits:\n\nCOWBORG - Cyber cowboy with cattle prod and shotgun\n\nSKYLORD - Hammer wielding warrior from beyond\n\nSKULL CZAR - Possessing dark energy sword and magic bow\n\nSABER SENTINAL - AR soldier with saber and pistol\n\nFor questions and feedback please join the Saber City Discord server: https://discord.gg/EhuQSbNeYV\n\nor contact via email: contact@yarwad.com\n\n", "short_description": "Saber City is a 2 player shared-space dueling game where players battle for supremacy in mixed-reality"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.yarwad.com/sabercityprivacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Yarwad Publishing Empire", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.yarwad.com/sabercity", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2710427532541308"}, {"id": "1436351953220286"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes":